City offices of William Morrow and Avon, which were closed 
Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
	News Corp. reportedly has held talks with several mid-sized  
players in its effort to expand its trade book publishing presence. 
The company had been talking with Viacom Inc. about merging 
HarperCollins with Viacom's Simon &AMP; Schuster, but those discussion 
broke off, the Reporter said, citing unidentified sources. 

  	   	
