<BODY>
<CATEGORY> entertainment </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Combs Performing on New Year's Eve </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	MIAMI (AP) -- Rap artist Sean ``Puffy'' Combs will perform at the  
Miami Arena on New Year's Eve, competing against another millennium 
eve party being thrown by Gloria Estefan a few blocks away. 
</P>
<P>
	Ms. Estefan will be performing at the American Airlines Arena,  
the new 20,000-seat downtown waterfront venue, with tickets ranging 
from $150 to $500. 
</P>
<P>
	The decade-old Miami Arena, a short walk from the new arena,  
booked Combs to headline the 17,000 seat venue Dec. 31, said Rob 
Franklin, general manager of the site. 
</P>
<P>
	``We are ready to compete,'' Franklin said. ``There is enough  
business to go around for everyone.'' 
</P>
<P>
	Ticket prices have not been set.  
  	   	
</P>
